# Mood Jaar — environment variables
#
# Paste the project's Google Gemini API key below (no quotes).
# Get a free key at: https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#
# NOTE: In a static/frontend-only build this value is embedded in the shipped
# JavaScript, so it can be extracted by visitors. Use a FREE Gemini key with
# NO billing enabled and set usage limits in Google AI Studio / Cloud console.

VITE_GEMINI_API_KEY=YOUR_API_KEY_HERE